<title>USA: Alexion gets $11.2 mln in private placement.</title>
<headline>Alexion gets $11.2 mln in private placement.</headline>
<dateline>NEW HAVEN, Conn. 1997-07-09</dateline>
<text>
<p>Alexion Pharmaceuticals Inc said Wednesday it received from institutional investors $11.2 million from the private placement of stock announced last month.</p>
<p>The company said proceeds from the previously announced private placement will be used to fund its research and development activities and for general corporate purposes.</p>
<p>Robertson, Stephens &amp; Co LLC was placement agent in the transaction.</p>
